message: "If you use this benchmark, harness, or its reference results, please cite the accompanying paper."
title: "Auditing Multi-Source Stock Prediction: An Evaluation Protocol and Benchmark"
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.21431362"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ltifi
    given-names: Mouadh
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0007-7456-0472"
